word to vector
go = [0.23, 0.48, 0.96 ... ] ...length is 300
similarly all words are converted to vector


how conversion is done

	- deciding the window size
	- skip gram modeling
	- pair with the words to make the training samples
	- each word is converted into one hot vector / or a dummy vector

https://mccormickml.com/2016/04/19/word2vec-tutorial-the-skip-gram-model/

one hot vector conversion have drawback that it does not differentiate as per the meaning, like bank can have many meaning.

test that the vector work

